  "comment": "EclProfile HD2 updates EclProfile HD ranges with extra brightness and higher CRI / R9 / TLCI. The fixture is a proper LED replacement for the traditional 750W Tungsten ellipsoidal luminaire. The optical system harnesses the power of a 230W COB LED to create an even beam with clean shutter cuts and beautiful sharp or soft edge gobo focusing. Featuring HD dimming and available in a 3.200 K or 5.700 K, the EclProfile HD2 delivers the performance and quality of output demanded from this level of the luminaire.",
